ncaa_fb_pbp

Source: R/ncaa_fb_pbp.R
ncaa_fb_pbp.Rd

Obtains the play by play info for a NCAA FB game

ncaa_fb_pbp(game_id)

Arguments

game_id

the game_id of a given NCAA FB game from the NCAA API

Value

a data frame of rows for each play in the game
